## üìñ What is Crypto-Sentry AI?

Crypto-Sentry AI started as my final year project - the goal was to build something that could actually help cryptocurrency traders spot unusual market activity before it becomes obvious.

Most crypto tools just show you prices and basic charts. I wanted to build something smarter that could actually understand market patterns and warn you when things look... weird.

The result is this full-stack application that combines real-time market data with a trained LSTM Autoencoder model to detect anomalies in cryptocurrency pricing and volume patterns.

## üéØ What It Actually Does

### For Regular Users:
- **Watch crypto prices** in real-time with interactive charts
- **Set up price alerts** for your favorite cryptocurrencies
- **Get AI-powered insights** about market conditions
- **Monitor multiple timeframes** from 1 day to 1 year

### The AI Magic:
- **Learns normal market behavior** from historical data
- **Spots unusual patterns** that might indicate manipulation or big moves
- **Gives confidence scores** so you know how reliable the detection is
- **Works in real-time** as new market data comes in

## ‚ú® Cool Features I Built

### üß† Smart AI Detection
- **Trained LSTM Autoencoder** that actually understands crypto market patterns
- **Real-time anomaly scoring** with confidence levels
- **Multiple cryptocurrency support** (BTC, ETH, ADA, and more)
- **Adaptive thresholds** that adjust to market volatility

### üìä Beautiful Dashboard
- **Interactive price charts** with volume overlays
- **Multiple timeframe views** (1D, 7D, 1M, 1Y)
- **Real-time market statistics** and trends
- **Professional trading-style interface**

### üîî Smart Alert System
- **Price target alerts** for specific levels
- **AI anomaly alerts** when the model detects something unusual
- **Trend direction alerts** for momentum changes
- **Email/push notifications** (ready for integration)

### üîê Secure & Scalable
- **JWT authentication** with proper security
- **SQLite database** (easy to switch to PostgreSQL)
- **RESTful API design** with proper documentation
- **Docker-ready** for easy deployment

## üõ† Tech Stack - Why I Chose These

### Frontend:
- **React + TypeScript** - For type safety and great developer experience
- **Tailwind CSS** - Because writing custom CSS for every component is tedious
- **Shadcn/ui** - Beautiful, accessible components out of the box
- **Recharts** - For those smooth, interactive charts

### Backend:
- **FastAPI** - Lightning fast with automatic API docs (seriously, it's amazing)
- **Python** - Because the AI/ML ecosystem is incredible
- **SQLAlchemy** - Database operations that don't make me want to cry
- **JWT Authentication** - Proper security without the headache

### AI/ML:
- **TensorFlow/Keras** - For building and training the LSTM model
- **Scikit-learn** - For data preprocessing and feature engineering
- **Pandas** - Because data manipulation should be easy
- **yFinance** - Free, reliable market data

### Infrastructure:
- **Docker** - So this actually runs on other people's machines
- **Docker Compose** - One command to rule them all
- **Nginx** - Fast, reliable static file serving

## üöÄ Quick Start - Get Running in 5 Minutes

### Prerequisites
- Docker and Docker Compose installed
- That's it. Seriously.

### The One-Command Setup
```bash
# Clone this repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/crypto-sentry-ai
cd crypto-sentry-ai

# Start everything up
docker-compose up
Wait a couple minutes (the first time takes a bit longer), then open your browser to:

