üö® Common Issues & Solutions
"API calls are failing / using demo data"
CoinGecko API has rate limits

The app automatically falls back to realistic demo data

This is normal and doesn't affect the AI functionality

"Docker compose is taking forever"
First build downloads all dependencies

Subsequent starts are much faster

Check if ports 3000 and 8000 are available

"AI model isn't loading"
Check the model files exist in backend/app/ai_model/model_artifacts/

The system falls back to Isolation Forest algorithm if LSTM fails

Both methods work well for anomaly detection

